<item>
            <title>[LU-7043] Interop 2.5.3&lt;-&gt;master conf-sanity test_86: Flex block group size: 256, expected: 1024</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7043</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah_lw &amp;lt;wei3.liu@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/f7353e42-4576-11e5-9d3c-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/f7353e42-4576-11e5-9d3c-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_86 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Flex block group size: 256, expected: 1024
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test log&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;CMD: shadow-21vm3 debugfs -c -R stats /dev/lvm-Role_OSS/P1
shadow-21vm3: debugfs 1.42.12.wc1 (15-Sep-2014)
shadow-21vm3: /dev/lvm-Role_OSS/P1: catastrophic mode - not reading inode or group bitmaps
 conf-sanity test_86: @@@@@@ FAIL: Flex block group size: 256, expected: 1024 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
